@@$TJvSplitter
<TITLE TJvSplitter overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
  TJvSplitter is a splitter control that supports extended features. 
  
  You can use OnMouseEnter and OnMouseLeave to alter the controls look or behavoir, when the user 
  moves the mouse pointer over the control.
  
  Property HintColor can be used to set a different color of the Help hint boxes for the splitter control.
