@@TJvSplitter
<GROUP TJvSplitter>
  Adds events that can be used for hot tracking.
Description
  You can use OnMouseEnter and OnMouseLeave to alter the controls look or behavoir, when the user 
  moves the mouse pointer over the control.

  Use property HintColor to change the color of the hint boxes for the scroll box.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvSplitter object.
Description
  Use Create to create and initialize a new TJvSplitter object.
  
  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the splitter control
  as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the splitter control.
See Also
  HintColor
