@@TJvSplitter.CMMouseEnter
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves over the splitter control.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves over the splitter control. It sets
  the hint color for the application to the property specified by HintColor, and triggers the 
  OnMouseEnter event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the splitter control of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseLeave, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.CMMouseLeave
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves off the splitter control.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves off the splitter control. It resets the
  hint color for the application, and triggers the OnMouseLeave event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the splitter control of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseEnter, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.CMParentColorChanged
Summary
  Responds when the color of the parent of the splitter control changes.
Description
  CMParentColorChanged is called automatically when the color of the parent of the splitter control changes.
  It triggers the OnParentColorChange event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the splitter control of the parent
        color change.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the hint boxes for the Help Hints for the splitter control.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. A default color value of clInfoBk is set for the
  HintColor property in the constructor when the application is created. To change the HintColor
  assign it a new TColor value.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.OnMouseEnter
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves over the splitter control.
Description
  Write an OnMouseEnter event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse over the
  splitter control. For example, you can use this event to change the font color when the mouse is over the
  splitter control, and then use the OnMouseLeave event to change it back when the mouse moves off the splitter control.
See Also
  OnMouseLeave 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the splitter control.
Description
  Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  splitter control. For example, you can use this event to undo changes that were made in an OnMouseEnter
  event handler.
See Also
  HotTrack, OnMouseEnter
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvSplitter.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color property for the parent of the splitter control changes.
Description
  Write an OnParentColorChange event to take specific action when the ParentColor property changes.
